description:
Tobey said that he likes "rednecks."
I don't know if I'd call Dave a redneck. I guess it depends on how you define it.
He's from a very small, rural, farm town, he's down to earth, he likes beer and baseball, and he's got a girlfriend who is clueless about his "extracurricular" activities.
Well, I guess that was enough for Tobey, but he LOVED Dave. I mean, absolutely loved him!
You could see that he was in heaven getting fucked by our muscle farm boy!
And as an added bonus, Dave eats some Tobey ass!
title: Dave & Tobey
